    <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-neutral-900 mb-3">Key Healthcare Considerations</h3>

    <div class="bg-amber-50 border border-amber-200 rounded-lg p-6 mb-6">
      <h4 class="font-semibold text-amber-900 mb-3">Small Island Limitations</h4>
      <ul class="space-y-2 text-amber-800">
        <li>• <strong>Specialist care:</strong> Some rare or complex conditions may require treatment in Italy, UK, or Germany</li>
        <li>• <strong>Equipment:</strong> Latest medical technology may not always be available locally</li>
